{
  "texts": [
    "To use transfer learning, CNNs are kept the same during the first training on the secondary domain.",
    "Only the layers that come after that are changed [150].The model that is being proposed is a combination of a CNN and explainable AI.",
    "Grad-CAM, LIME, and SHAP are used to analyze and describe the information for more understanding.",
    "The extraction of convolutional features is used to gather high-level, object-based data.",
    "Next, the CNN model's black-box technique is assessed utilizing shapely information from SHAP, predictive results from LIME, and a heat map from Grad-CAM [151].A two-step ML-based diagnostic and predictive model was designed."
  ]
}